title: Le Tour de France 2014 - officials press kit and roadbook

Cycling : Le Tour de France 2014 - officials press kit and roadbook

Name :			101st edition Tour de France 2014
Fight for Yellow jersey (officials press kit and roadbook)
Release date :		2014-06-17
Publisher :		A.S.O. (Amaury Sport Organisation)
Official site : <a href="	http://www.letour.fr" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">	http://www.letour.fr</a> , @letour and #TDF
File size :		321,13 MB
Book Language :		French and English
Press kit title :	TDF14_DP-PaP.indd
Pages :			press kit - 58 and roadbook - 209
File type :		PDF
Dimensions :		press kit - 594x708 and roadbook - 594x841
Security method :	None
Content creator :	press kit - Adobe InDesign CS6 (Macintosh) and
roadbook - Adobe InDesign CC (Macintosh)(Foxit Advanced PDF Editor)
Encoding software :	press kit - Adobe PDF Library 10.0.1 and
roadbook - Adobe PDF Library 11.0
Real size :		press kit - 8,95Mb and roadbook - 312.18Mb

Note :	Officials press kit and roadbook from Leeds (England) to Paris
(France), these are the 21 stages, teams, sponsors and more information
of Le Tour de France 2014 (start from 05th July 2014 to 27th July 2014).

The Stages :
- nine flat stages ,
- five fill stages ,
- six mountain stages and five altitude finishes ,
- one ITT (individual time-trial) stage ,
- two rest days ,
+ TOTAL AVANT HOMOLOGATION : 3 656 kilometers.
